{{bottom}}

===Etymology 2===
From Old French [[volter]], from a frequentative form of Latin [[volvere]] ‘turn, roll’; later assiliated to Etymology 1, above.

====Verb====
{{en-verb}}

# ''(transitive and intransitive)'' To jump or leap over (something).

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# An act of vaulting; a [[leap]] or [[jump]].

